OpenCL-OCaml is OCaml binding for OpenCL.  It closely follows the OpenCL specification.
It currently implements the functionality needed for performing computations.  Other calls
can be implemented when they're needed.

Building
------------------
To build the library do:

    make

If OpenCL library cannot be found modify Makefile's OPENCL_LIB_DIR.

To build examples and documentation do:

    make examples
    make doc
